column5: Hey guys,  Thought I would post on here that the winner of two tickets to the Spring Fishing & Boat Show on Facebook is Lorne Morley. I believe he is a certain carp angler on here. Congrats!  A small change aswell, we are now at booth #1629. Still in the main hall, you can't miss us   Huge thanks to the mods here for letting us do this
Congrats Lorne and thank you for the initiative, Dan. Great job!
